data.name: About Us
data.rich_text:
Common Point Communications, LLC (Common Point) specializes in risk communication, crisis management, and marketing communications to support continued progress. Our Agile PR approach is about people and relationships. Metrics focus on impacts and outcomes over budget justification. Our region’s strong federal, state and local government presence drives the Common Point mission to support the public good through communication that is ethical, effective, and seeks common understanding.
 
  • Strategic research and planning
  • Message and audience mapping
  • Stakeholder relations
  • Internal communications
  • Speaker and media training
  • Crisis communications planning and risk management
  • Executive image coaching
  • Media relations
  • Digital media development
  • Technical, opinion and bylined article writing
  • Proposal support

data.detail: Even after shutting down in 2012, a 2,700 MW nuclear generating station on the west coast continues to face challenges from opponents in and around the community. We monitor the issues, influencers, and backers to help guide proactive community engagement to promote common goals.
data.excerpt: Even after shutting down in 2012, a 2,700 MW nuclear generating station on the west coast continues.
data.name: Issues Monitoring and Intel

data.detail: An edge data center and interconnection provider was looking to develop a content marketing strategy to support BD and market expansion efforts across multiple regions of the U.S. We develop eBooks, guides, blogs and visual narratives to engage and educate, generate interest, and qualify leads.
data.excerpt: An edge data center and interconnection provider was looking to develop a content marketing strategy
data.name: Content Marketing Strategy

data.detail: A non-profit collaborative produced a first-of-its-kind report funded by the U.S. Department of Commerce, Economic Development Agency on socioeconomic impacts of power plant closures on communities across the country. We worked with the client to develop messaging, craft a press release and generate national and international media coverage to raise awareness and pave the way for the next phase of technical assistance and best-practice resources.
